quran[34]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,17,"Wakitumikiwa na wavulana wa ujana wa milele, <sup>17</sup>","[17] Wakiwazungukia kwa kuwakhudumia vijana watakao baki milele hivyo hivyo,"
  56,18,"Kwa vikombe na mabirika na bilauri za vinywaji kutoka chemchem safi. <sup>18</sup>","[18] Nao wamechukua vikombe na mabirika yaliyo jaa vinywaji vya Peponi, na bilauri zenye mvinyo kutoka chemchem zinazo miminika,"
  56,19,"Hawataumwa kichwa kwa vinywaji hivyo wala hawatoleweshwa. <sup>19</sup>","[19] Vinywaji hivyo haviwaletei kuumwa kichwa wala kutokwa akili kwa ulevi."
  56,20,"Na matunda wayapendayo, <sup>20</sup>","[20] Na matunda ya kila namna wanayo yapenda na wanayo yaona;"
  56,21,"Na nyama za ndege kama wanavyo tamani. <sup>21</sup>","[21] Na nyama za ndege kama zinavyo tamani nafsi zao."
  56,22,"Na Mahurulaini, <sup>22</sup>","[22] Na wanawake wenye macho ya vikombe,"
  56,23,"Walio kama mfano wa lulu zilio hifadhiwa. <sup>23</sup>","[23] Kama mfano wa lulu zilio hifadhiwa katika chaza, kwa usafi wao na urembo wao."
  56,24,"Ni malipo kwa waliyo kuwa wakiyatenda. <sup>24</sup>","[24] Watapewa haya kuwa ni malipo kwa mambo mema waliyo kuwa wakiyatenda duniani."
  56,25,"Humo hawatasikia porojo wala maneno ya dhambi, <sup>25</sup>","[25] Huko Peponi hawatasikia maneno yasiyo kuwa na maana, wala masimulizi ya kumtia dhambini mwenye kuyasikia."
  56,26,"Isipo kuwa maneno ya Salama, Salama. <sup>26</sup>","[26] Ila watalo sikia ni kauli ya wao kwa wao: Tunakusalimuni kwa Salama."
  56,27,"Na wale wa mkono wa kulia, ni yepi yatakuwa ya wa kuliani? <sup>27</sup>","[27] Na watu wa mkono wa kulia, hapana ajuaye nini malipo ya watu wa kuliani."
  56,28,"Katika mikunazi isiyo na miba, <sup>28</sup>","[28] Katika miti ya mikunazi iliyo katwa miba yake,"
  56,29,"Na migomba iliyo pangiliwa, <sup>29</sup>","[29] Na migomba iliyo pangika na ndizi zake zimepandana juu ya mikungu,"
  56,30,"Na kivuli kilicho tanda, <sup>30</sup>","[30] Na kivuli kilicho enea wala hakiondoki,"
  56,31,"Na maji yanayo miminika, <sup>31</sup>","[31] Na maji yanayo miminika karibu yao popote wayatakapo,"
  56,32,"Na matunda mengi, <sup>32</sup>","[32] Na matunda ya namna nyingi na kabila nyingi yasiyo tindikia wakati wowote,"
  56,33,"Hayatindikii wala hayakatazwi, <sup>33</sup>","[33] Wala hazuiwiliwi ayatakayo,"
  56,34,"Na matandiko yaliyo nyanyuliwa. <sup>34</sup>","[34] Na matandiko yaliyo nyanyuliwa ya starehe."
  56,35,"Hakika Sisi tutawaumba (Mahurulaini) upya, <sup>35</sup>","[35] Hakika Sisi tulianza kuwaumba Mahurulaini mwanzo,"
  56,36,"Na tutawafanya vijana, <sup>36</sup>","[36] Na tukawafanya kuwa ni vijana,"
  56,37,"Wanapendana na waume zao, hirimu moja. <sup>37</sup>","[37] Wenye kupendwa na waume zao, wenye umri ulio karibiana,"
  56,38,"Kwa ajili ya watu wa kuliani. <sup>38</sup>","[38] Wa tayari kwa neema ya watu wa kuliani."
  56,39,"Fungu kubwa katika wa mwanzo, <sup>39</sup>","[39] Watu wa kulia ni wengi katika mataifu yaliyo kwisha tangulia,"
  56,40,"Na fungu kubwa katika wa mwisho. <sup>40</sup>","[40] Na kikundi kikubwa katika umma wa Muhammad."
  56,41,"Na watu wa kushotoni; je ni yepi ya wa kushotoni? <sup>41</sup>","[41] Na watu wa kushoto, hapana anaye jua nini adhabu ya watu wa kushoto."
  56,42,"Katika upepo wa moto, na maji yanayo chemka, <sup>42</sup>","[42] Watakuwa kwenye upepo umoto utakao wazunguka, unao penya katika tundu za mwili, na maji yaliyo chemshwa motoni wayanywe na wamiminiwe vichwani,"
  56,43,"Na kivuli cha moshi mweusi, <sup>43</sup>","[43] Na katika kivuli cha kiza cheusi cha moshi umoto,"
  56,44,"Si cha kuburudisha wala kustarehesha. <sup>44</sup>","[44] Hapana ubaridi wa kupunguza joto la hewa, wala huruma ya kuwaletea nafuu wanapo vuta pumzi."
  56,45,"Hakika hao walikuwa kabla ya haya wakiishi maisha ya anasa. <sup>45</sup>","[45] Hakika hao kabla ya haya walikuwa wamepita kiasi katika kustarehea neema za duniani, wamepumbaa hawataki kumt'ii Mwenyezi Mungu Mtukufu."
  56,46,"Na walikuwa wakishikilia kufanya madhambi makubwa, <sup>46</sup>","[46] Na walikuwa wameshikilia daima kufanya dhambi kubwa kabisa, kwani waliapa kwa Mwenyezi Mungu kwamba kabisa Mwenyezi Mungu hatamfufua aliye kufa."
  56,47,"Na walikuwa wakisema: Tutakapo kufa na tukawa udongo na mafupa, ati ndio tutafufuliwa? <sup>47</sup>","[47] Na walikuwa wakisema kwa kukanusha kurejea tena: Ati tutafufuliwa baada ya kwisha kufa, na baadhi ya miili yetu ikisha kuwa udongo na mengine mifupa iliyo chakaa? Ati sisi tutarudishwa tuwe hai mara ya pili?"
  56,48,"Au baba zetu wa zamani? <sup>48</sup>","[48] Ati tutafufuliwa sisi na baba zetu wa zamani walio kwisha kuwa udongo ulio tapanyika na umepotea katika ardhi?"
  56,49,"Sema: Hakika wa zamani na wa mwisho <sup>49</sup>","[49] Waambie kwa kuwajibu kukanusha kwao: Hakika wa zamani na wa mwisho, ambao nyinyi ni katika jumla ya hao,"
  56,50,"Bila ya shaka watakusanywa kwa wakati wa siku maalumu. <sup>50</sup>","[50] Nyote mtakusanywa katika wakati wa siku malumu, na wala hamtoipita."
